FW East Powerpst Tina Rode Assistant to Dave Duran Cell Original Message From Duran W David Sent Tuesday July AM To Rode Tina Subject FW East Power Original Message From Duran W David Sent Monday July PM To Kitchen Louise Subject East Power Louise Here are some bullet points for the discussions tomorrow East Power including Generation Investments made about million in the first half The greatest contribution came from Ben Jacoby about million By the way I hired Ben along with Scott Healy to acquire sites in All of the traders and structuring including Bernie Aucoin told me that John Llodra drove both the CMP and NStar deals Total income million I believe Delainey was correct in saying that Ozzie was the brains behind Alamac but Heather did the execution Total income for the East million Most of the rest of the deals were done after I came in Mid market sales have increased over the first half of This group was in meltdown when I came inat least on the origination side I would like to get some credit for stopping the bleeding and starting the rebuilding process in a difficult environment

Vepco Meeting Cc Please plan on attend a meeting on Monday November at am in conference room EBB From Rahil This meeting is to discuss our contract with VEPCO and the relevant issues surrounding that deal Dave had requested this meeting when I spoke with him last week and Ive already mentioned this to Kevin Elizabeth and Heather Checked with Richard Sanders office and his Monday afternoon is fairly open for now Pls call me if you have any questions I will be traveling but will have my cell phone and email You may want to contact Heather if there is some urgent matter Thanks in advance Rahil Cell
